            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_104wh' title='Col. 104WH &mdash; HC Deb 17 January 2001 vol 361 c104WH' name='column_104wh' href='#column_104wh' rel='bookmark'>104WH</a>
            problems endemic to Wales and Merseyside that we need to sort out. The problems are often different, and there is a difference of emphasis and degree of difficulty and so on.
          </p>
